HEADWORD: mamas boy
<hw>mama's boy</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A boy excessively attached to his
mother; a boy lacking the usual masculine interests; also spelled
<asp>mamma's boy</asp>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mother's boy.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

